  "title": "Service Technician |Basic up to $3400 |5 Days - ZH",
  "description": "<p>Location: Island wide, Reporting at Pioneer (Office)<br />Salary: Basic up to $3400<br />Working Days: (8.15am-5.15pm)<br /><br />Key Duties:</p><ul><li>Maintain, service, and overhaul compressed air systems, including compressors and dryers.</li><li>Troubleshoot, repair faults, and perform equipment testing and commissioning.</li><li>Monitor client compressor usage and provide performance and maintenance recommendations.</li><li>Prepare quotations and manage new or renewal service contracts.</li></ul><p>Key Requirements:</p><ul><li>Min. Nitec in Mechanical Servicing, Mechanical Engineering, or Relevant</li><li>Min. 1 years relevant experience</li><li>Valid class 3 driving license</li></ul><p>WhatsApp me at wa.me/6587801169 or press the APPLY NOW BUTTON.</p><p>By submitting your resume and/or personal information, you consent to the collection, use, and disclosure of your personal data by the company (or its designated agent) for the purposes of processing, administration and managing your job application.</p><p>Please be notified that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Sim Shu Hui Reg No.: R25129789<br />Griffin HR Consultancy Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 23C1449</p>",
